	(text "Sensors — pinout (U5 LIS3DHTR, LGA-16).  PLACED, not wired.\nU5 LIS3DH:\n  1  VDD_IO   +3V3 (C24 100nF)        9  INT2     NC  (2nd alarm removed)\n  2  NC                              10  RES      -> GND\n  3  NC                              11  INT1     -> PA2 (wake + tamper, OR via CTRL_REG3 I1_IA2)\n  4  SCL      -> PB6 (I2C1)          12  GND      GND\n  5  GND      GND                    13  ADC3     NC\n  6  SDA      -> PB7 (I2C1)          14  VDD      +3V3 (C23 100nF)\n  7  SDO/SA0  addr 0x18(GND)/0x19    15  ADC2     NC\n  8  CS       +3V3 (force I2C)       16  ADC1     NC\nI2C1:  R9/R10 4.7k pull-ups to +3V3_SW (GATED).   Load switch Q3 AO3401A hi-side + Q4 AO3400A gate-drv +\n  R30 gate-PU + R31 PERI_EN-PD + C31 1uF; PERI_EN (PA3, act-hi) gates DS1 + U7 + R9/R10 so nothing leaks in\n  Stop.  U5 stays on always-on +3V3 (wake); FW drives PB6/PB7 LOW before Stop so the powered accel never sees\n  the unpulled bus.  Tamper now on INT1 (CTRL_REG3 I1_IA2); may zeroize the TOTP secret (DESIGN.md Security)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
